messages.message: Hi @prateek.tenkale not sure if this is due to your local tests, but feel free to play with the app I created to reproduce the issue. You want want to delete the fields for each class to test the case ‘not showing in review tab for class confidence < t’, and recreate the fields again to test the case ‘showing in review tab for class/field confidence < t’’: https://aihub.instabase.com/build/01968c91-b75a-7fbc-8a92-88a333df73ed (https://aihub.instabase.com/build/01968c91-b75a-7fbc-8a92-88a333df73ed)
